*Loša* vremenska prognoza (The weather forecast is bad.)
Njegovo ponašanje je *loše* ocenjeno od strane profesora (His behavior was rated badly by the professor.)
Ona se oseća *loše* oko toga što se desilo (She feels bad about what happened.)
*Loša* vest je stigla do nas preko medija (The bad news arrived to us through the media.)
*Lošije* je bilo prošle godine (It was worse last year.)